                            <comment id="115744" author="ckristo" created="Sun, 17 May 2015 11:51:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I experience the same problem when using XML-only JPA config (via orm.xml). The problem seems to reside in the code that generates the link to an element. It tries to fetch the entity&apos;s ID property which is null when using XML-only JPA config because Spring Data JPA&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;JpaPersistentPropertyImpl.isIdProperty()&lt;/tt&gt; just checks for annotations to determine if a JPA property is an ID property or not. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
